thread.title: BRIEF-Prothena Q4 Loss Per Share $1.24

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Prothena Q4 Loss Per Share $1.24
text:
Feb 14 (Reuters) - Prothena Corporation Plc:
* PROTHENA REPORTS FOURTH QUARTER AND FULL YEAR 2017 FINANCIAL RESULTS, AND PROVIDES FINANCIAL GUIDANCE AND RESEARCH AND DEVELOPMENT UPDATE
* Q4 LOSS PER SHARE $1.24 * Q4 REVENUE $200,000 * AS OF DECEMBER 31, 2017, PROTHENA HAD $421.7 MILLION IN CASH, CASH EQUIVALENTS AND RESTRICTED CASH AND NO DEBT
* EXPECTS THE FULL YEAR 2018 NET CASH BURN FROM OPERATING AND INVESTING ACTIVITIES TO BE $175 TO $230 MILLION
* Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $-1.48, REVENUE VIEW $237600.00 -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
